statement_latex:
Find the norm and condition number of

\begin{align*}
\begin{bmatrix}
0  & 2 \\ 1 & 0
\end{bmatrix} = \left( \begin{bmatrix}
0 & 1 \\ 1 & 0
\end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix}
1 & 0 \\ 0 & 2
\end{bmatrix} \right)
\end{align*}

statement_raw:
Find the norm and condition number of
:&lt;math>
\begin{bmatrix}
0  &amp; 2 \\ 1 &amp; 0
\end{bmatrix} = \left( \begin{bmatrix}
0 &amp; 1 \\ 1 &amp; 0
\end{bmatrix} \begin{bmatrix}
1 &amp; 0 \\ 0 &amp; 2
\end{bmatrix} \right)
&lt;/math>
